        <abstract>
            <p>After all, CD is now beginning to prepare an abstract of his species theory. Recounts the events leading to joint paper with A. R. Wallace at Linnean Society. Lyell and Hooker urge strongly that he publish a fuller abstract. It is impossible to do justice to subject in an abstract.</p>
            <p>His sister, Marianne Parker, has died.</p>
        </abstract>
